de-Arquitectura-Mexico-12a-800x1120.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-12a-768x1075.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-12a-1097x1536.jpg 1097w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-12a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=555685\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-555685\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-13a-810x506.jpg\" alt=\"Modern open-concept living space with wooden furniture, large windows, and an outdoor dining area visible through sliding glass doors. A comfortable couch, indoor plants, and a bookshelf are featured.\" width=\"810\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-13a-810x506.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-13a-800x500.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-13a-768x480.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-13a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOn the ground floor, the main volume houses communal spaces like the sunken living room and dining area, which seamlessly open to a terrace and garden. The upper level contains the primary suite, complete with a walk-in closet and private garden, creating a secluded retreat within the home. The other three volumes accommodate a range of functions, including a study, guest rooms, a gym, and secondary bedrooms. These areas are carefully arranged to maximize privacy and natural light, utilizing vertical greenery and latticework to form a sense of division without the need for shared walls.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=555686\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-555686\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-14a-810x506.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room features a large sectional sofa, round coffee tables, a spacious dining table with chairs, and a wall of floor-to-ceiling bookshelves, with large windows showcasing an outdoor garden.\" width=\"810\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-14a-810x506.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-14a-800x500.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-14a-768x480.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-14a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=555687\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-555687\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-15a-810x1048.jpg\" alt=\"A modern dining area with a long black table, wooden chairs, and framed art on the walls. Large windows reveal outdoor greenery; wooden ceiling panels and indoor plants add to the contemporary decor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1048\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-15a-810x1048.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-15a-800x1035.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-15a-768x994.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-15a-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-15a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=555688\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-555688\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-16a-810x506.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen and living area with neutral tones, wooden accents, and minimalist design. A person is blurred in motion near the sink.\" width=\"810\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-16a-810x506.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-16a-800x500.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-16a-768x480.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-16a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe residence employs strategic placement of load-bearing walls and grilles to mitigate solar exposure and optimize ventilation, reducing the need for artificial cooling systems and promoting energy savings. The garden-facing facade opens up to the lush landscape, fostering a strong connection to nature, while the street-facing facade remains more closed, ensuring privacy and controlled natural lighting.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=555689\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-555689\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-17a-810x1048.jpg\" alt=\"A modern interior space with large glass windows, wooden walls, and floors. There is a small table with chairs near the windows, overlooking green foliage outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1048\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-17a-810x1048.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-17a-800x1035.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-17a-768x994.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-17a-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-17a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=555690\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-555690\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-18a-810x1134.jpg\" alt=\"A narrow corridor with brick walls and a large window at the end, offering a view of a cityscape and sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1134\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-18a-810x1134.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-18a-800x1120.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-18a-768x1075.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-18a-1097x1536.jpg 1097w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-18a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=555691\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-555691\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-19a-810x1134.jpg\" alt=\"Person standing on a terrace with planters, looking out at a cityscape during sunset.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1134\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-19a-810x1134.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-19a-800x1120.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-19a-768x1075.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-19a-1097x1536.jpg 1097w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-19a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=555692\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-555692\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-20a-810x506.jpg\" alt=\"Modern two-story house with large windows, an outdoor dining area, and a spacious lawn in the foreground.\" width=\"810\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-20a-810x506.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-20a-800x500.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-20a-768x480.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/08/Casa-Catedral-Laboratorio-de-Arquitectura-Mexico-20a.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTo see more from Laboratorio de Arquitectura, follow them on Instagram \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/laboratoriodearquitectura/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ariadnapolo.foto/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eAriadna Polo\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
